<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF636ADCFA8490AD18BBBC09" pageId="152" pageNumber="913" type="activity">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF636ADCFA8490AD18BBBC09" blockId="152.[1400,2612,872,2088]" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF636ADCFA8490AD1867BC27" bold="true" box="[1400,1639,1780,1813]" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Found roosting under tree bark, in dry banana leaves, and in the bases of banana plants.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF636ADCFA85911A179EBC56" box="[1401,2462,1859,1892]" pageId="152" pageNumber="913" type="biology_ecology">
